Molajo will automatically load CSS and JS files placed into the following folders, as follows:

1. Application-specific CSS and JS in => media/site/[application]/css[js]/XYZ.css[js]
2. Component specific CSS and JS in => media/site/[application]/[com_component]/css[js]/XYZ.css[js]
3. Asset ID (for the page) specific CSS and JS in => media/site/[application]/[asset_id]/css[js]/XYZ.css[js]

Note:

a. Layouts also have CSS and JS folders within the Layout Extension to be used for automatically
loading media files. Layouts are located in => layouts/[type]/[layout_name]
b. Name Right-to-left CSS files with rtl_ prefix for Molajo to automatic load, when needed.
